data.description: A real dollhouse!!  The Chesapeake Bay is just down the street!  Big covered front porch!  Brand new white kitchen cabinets and quartz counter tops!  Stainless appliances in the kitchen.  Finished 2nd floor has one bedroom and another room that could be a 4th bedroom.  Big den on back of house with brick fireplace and closet with barn0style door.  Second fireplace in Living room. Deck.  Storage shed.  Big backyard.
